<h2>featured member</h2>
<h2><span style="font-size: 1.3em; text-align: justify; color: #000000; line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp;</span><a href="http://actp-ptca.ca/" target="_blank"><span style="font-size: 1.3em; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.6em;"><img style="vertical-align: middle;" src="/images/stories/logos/ACTP_logo_final.jpg" alt="ACTP logo_final" width="150" height="80" /></span></a></h2>
<p class="featured-desc" style="width: 308px; height: 92px; text-align: justify;">The Atlantic Canada Tourism Partnership bring together the Atlantic Canada Opportunities Agency, the provincial departments responsible for tourism in New Brunswick, Newfoundland &amp; Labrador, Nova Scotia and Prince Edward Island and the four provincial tourism industry associations. <a href="http://actp-ptca.ca/" target="_blank">Read More</a></p>
